cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address to an invalid IP format (999.999.999.999) will cause AMF connection failure and NG interface issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_dtx_threshold to an out-of-range value (1000) will cause invalid PRACH DTX configuration and RACH procedure failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_dtx_threshold 設定為超出範圍的值 (1000)，會導致無效的 PRACH DTX 配置，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
